### Markdown Formatting Examples
```markdown
# H1 Header
## H2 Header
### H3 Header
- Use horizontal rules (`---`) and headers (`##`) to organize tips.
- Bullet point
1. Numbered list

---

- Bullet point
1. Numbered list
